snippet.title: The Legacy of Kain Series: Blood Omen 2 - Video Game Trailer. (2002) PC/PS2/GC/XBox.
snippet.description:
The Legacy of Kain Series: Blood Omen 2. 
video game trailer.
Developed by Crystal Dynamics fot Playstation 2.
Published by Eidos Interactive in spring 2002 for Playstation2, PC Windows and Xbox, then in late 2002/early 2003 for GameCube..
Windows, Xbox and GameCube versions ported by Nixxes Software.
